title: Nature's Creatures
description: An illustration featuring a sequence of natural elements: a tuft of green grass, a grasshopper, a green frog, and a fox. The images are arranged from left to right, showcasing a variety of life forms in a natural setting.

title: Wildlife Collection
description: An illustration featuring various animals and plants. The top row includes a peregrine falcon and a hawk. The middle row shows a squirrel, a mouse, a blackbird, and a grasshopper. The bottom row features a green frog, a snail, and a snake, along with a cluster of colorful plants and flowers.
